Summary: Rotating circular object spinning and blinking lights hovers and takes a path down I-95
divs: sighting detailsi was on my way home from work on 12\22\2011 traveling i-95 through howard county and baltimore county, md heading northbound. when out of no where a large beam of light appeared and from light came a object which appeared to be round and spinning rapidly with blinking bright white lights. i believe that there were just a few lights that were colored (red, blue, green) but mainly all white on the unidentified object. i watched it go past my car on the left side. i almost felt like it was just a few feet away. as it went by i looked in my rear view mirror to make sure that it was still there. i could see it heading south down i-95 toward the elkridge (howard county)area.
